The paper discusses the application of deep reinforcement learning in autonomous driving systems, which involves artificial intelligence (AI) and robotics (RO) techniques. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms (LG) and computer vision (CV) in autonomous driving systems. Additionally, the paper addresses the challenges of deploying autonomous driving systems, which involves systems and control (SY) techniques.
